OL,5, The Oscar-winning Iranian film-maker   
OL,6, Asghar Farhadi has been summoned to    
OL,7, appear in court in Iran over           
OL,8, accusations of plagiarism.             
OL,10,FA former student of Farhadi, Azadeh    
OL,11,FMasihzadeh, claims he stole the idea   
OL,12,Ffor his latest film, A Hero, from her  
OL,13,Fdocumentary, All Winners All Losers.   
OL,15,FHe denies this, saying that he         
OL,16,Fresearched the story independently.    
OL,18,FFarhadi won Academy Awards for Best    
OL,19,FInternational Feature for A Separation,
OL,20,Fin 2012 and The Salesman in 2017.      
